values:
I am in the process of photographically documenting how tormenting my roommate, Tom Cruise (see previous posts such as Bitch Please, Part One, Two, and Three), can be for me to live with. Who couldn't agree about shitty roommates, I certainly have laughed a lot about the antics Ash's roommates create. I just thought it could be funny to share, plus some day I will look back and say, &quot;Oh! This is why I can't live with other people anymore. I forgot until...&quot;

This process has caused me to take photos of my room. I would like to not live in one room alone, and I feel this is the same room restated/reinvented from previous years, but most of the items are nostalgic inducing items I cannot part with, and so they go back up periodically. I will post them as well sometime soonish.

And now I'm off to read for class and dream of what things the Obama Administration will accomplish starting tomorrow! Huzzah. Lucky Obama kids, they get a puppy.
